name: Diamond
description: I’m very patient, purposeful and generous. I’m sincere and open person as I prefer to have equal relations..I enjoy going in for sport very much, mountain skiing, tennis, swimming and training. I’m here to find my special one who will respect me and love me. I’m sure people always can find compromises in any situation but you just need to believe in this.. I’m highly looking for with a stable position in life. Must love and be faithful and hope leads a healthy lifestyle and has normal interests that we may share
